.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has constantly talked of being ready to walk away from top-flight tennis with the caveat that he would play on if his body allowed.\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top-flight tennis\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3549}, {\"ngram\": \"the caveat\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"his body\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tomorrow might be when it finally ends but, with Murray, who really knows, and the performance was night and day from round one, where they looked for much of it like they had never stepped on a court together.\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3659, \"end\": 3665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.427418404951997e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tomorrow\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3618}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3704}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3714}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"a court\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Murray, Evans wears his heart on his sleeve and, like his playing partner, started to dream of what had been unthinkable a few weeks ago.\", \"from\": 3822, \"to\": 3964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3827, \"end\": 3833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.427418404951997e-40, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], 